              <tr> 
                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Advanced Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Pure Energy</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.73)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=25012">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9260">Jamie "XwarlocK" Kelly</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9260&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Infinite energy combo deck that took 2nd place in the 2002 MND World Championship at GenCon.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> August 12, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Pure Energy<br>
<br>
Magi:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(526)">Aula</a>  (Start: <a href="javascript:card_browser(521)">J&#39;lith</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(348)">Cloud Sceptre</a>)<br>
Obgren  (Start: Bog Stone)<br>
Shaper&#39;s Apprentice  (Start: <a href="javascript:card_browser(441)">Sea Barl</a>, Greater <a href="javascript:card_browser(708}<a href="javascript:card_browser({377)">Gar</a>gagnor</a>)<br>
<br>
Creatures: 10<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(521)">J&#39;lith</a> x1<br>
Quido Swarm x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(441)">Sea Barl</a> x1<br>
Bubble <a href="javascript:card_browser(337)">Xyx</a> x3<br>
Greater <a href="javascript:card_browser(708}<a href="javascript:card_browser({377)">Gar</a>gagnor</a> x1<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(476)">Ormagon</a> x1<br>
<br>
Relics: 12<br>
Warrior Boots x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(734)">Climbing Staff</a> x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(678)">Abraxin&#39;s Crown</a> x1<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(652)">Rayje&#39;s Belt</a> x1<br>
Bog Stone x1<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(348)">Cloud Sceptre</a> x1<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(529)">Abwyn&#39;s Quill</a> x1<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(650)">Mantle of Shadows</a> x1<br>
<br>
Spells: 18<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(745)">Kybar&#39;s Echo</a> x3<br>
